; The tape shim: implements Jane Street's splittable_random interface,
; delegating to the vendored real implementation (sr_real), but
; recording/replaying every draw as a typed tape choice when a tape is
; installed via For_tape. Owning the `splittable_random` name in this
; workspace makes the vendored base_quickcheck compile against us.
(library
 (name splittable_random)
 (libraries base tape sr_real))
